{"tid":1700044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班狗肯定問緊領展拎緊cam 睇","createTime":"2019-11-08T09:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T12:14:14.000Z","uid":128348,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bed9c2bd912d66efa8237297a12d1264ea6a2fec","tid":1700044,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:45:00.000Z","msg":"地鐵想封站 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aAAqdu3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaAAqdu3.png&h=a4fa9a15&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n班狗一定會搵領展傾<br />\n上次公開幾段片都已經見到有人推人<br />\n如果再公開晒 班狗一定驚到傻<br />\n所以如果領展今晚都唔公開就肯定係班狗㩒住<br />\n等edit 完再公開<br />\n<br />\n街坊如果你住果個位見到停車場/ 案發現場 <br />\n最好今晚拎住部cam set 定影住"},{"pid":"70161fdce5b622174d824c200d2662694c6fb6a6","tid":1700044,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:45:26.000Z","msg":"班狗知道比你地入去實會搵到料"},{"pid":"0b172064dc1f61fe018a7263fedfc397d38bd11a","tid":1700044,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"佢唔會比領展就咁公開cam"},{"pid":"2bd53c79a768224b2fb3badab1bbf5933698fe9b","tid":1700044,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:46:33.000Z","msg":"一定要迫領展今晚公開cam"},{"pid":"cf275deb104b8f8be93861f0f76b98ad71353d76","tid":1700044,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"佢話公開都係驚比人裝修趺股價姐<br />\n話公開又唔公開/公開啲垃圾既<br />\n咁佢就好至為知啦"},{"pid":"c7e32c55e6ae8add3c83dc016953fce64c056128","tid":1700044,"uid":529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:49:04.000Z","msg":"最多係俾狗睇先/狗睇完話公開得先公開<br />\n改cctv就唔會啦 要改條郁緊既片 點改<br />\n一陣俾人發現到 肯定慘過唔公開 點會同你搏"},{"pid":"5c23fb6b5e3868f5e71bdb4175caac2fde3c24c2","tid":1700044,"uid":132888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"隔離post唔係話星期二已經有搜查令攞晒黎睇啦咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f937980966b9cbc2972c3